column5: Ok, so am I the only one that is feeling old looking at these guys?    That's a lot of years on the water right there.    Any idea when each of them had their first show on TV?  I think I watched all of them.

I know Fish'n Canada started back in 1986 (so 34 years ago), Started with Reno & Angelo, Pete never came on as a host alongside them till later, his first appearance (named appearance anyway, not sure if he could be seen in the background of other episodes) was Episode 10 of 13 in Season 1 (1986) I'm not sure how old Pete is, but assuming late teens/early 20's back then, he sure looks good for being in his 50's i'm assuming.
When I tell people I am 55, they say no way . Took you for maybe 45-47. LOL
